l.%20He%20wants%20the%20judge%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-vs-openai-sam-altman-legal-battle-stakes-microsoft-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereverse%20OpenAI's%20corporate%20transformation%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20kick%20Altman%20and%20Brockman%20out%20of%20the%20organization's%20leadership%2C%20and%20disgorge%20it%20of%20%26quot%3Ball%20ill-gotten%20gains%26quot%3B%20from%20its%20for-profit%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGonzalez%20Rogers%20said%20she'll%20determine%20the%20remedies%20at%20a%20later%20stage%20if%20the%20jury%20finds%20Altman%2C%20Brockman%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20liable%20in%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20jury%20finds%20Altman%20not%20liable%20for%20the%20allegations%20Musk%20has%20brought%20against%20him%2C%20then%20it%20would%20demonstrate%20that%20nine%20ordinary%20people%20in%20California%2C%20at%20least%2C%20would%20have%20found%20him%20pretty%20trustworthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-takes-sam-altman-credibility-to-court-openai-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777197001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ebd30c3fecbb42897a3eb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-takes-sam-altman-credibility-to-court-openai-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20lawsuit%20against%20Sam%20Altman%20asks%20jurors%20to%20dig%20into%20grievances%20that%20stretch%20back%20to%20OpenAI's%20founding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lungi%20Ngidi's%20first%20words%20after%20horrific%20injury%20in%20DC%20vs%20PBKS%20clash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777196665000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.t