c8fdc096e994%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221421%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPortland%20Trail%20Blazers%20owner%20Tom%20Dundon%20is%20slashing%20costs%20after%20paying%20billions%20to%20buy%20the%20NBA%20franchise.%3Cp%3ESoobum%20Im%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPortland%20Trail%20Blazers%20owner%20billionaire%20Tom%20Dundon%20is%20generating%20lots%20of%20headlines%20for%20his%20cost-cutting.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20businessman's%20style%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20hardcore%20culture%20that%20is%20spreading%20across%20tech%20and%20the%20wider%20business%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMark%20Cuban%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20era%20of%20increasingly%20expensive%20franchises%20adds%20pressure%20to%20position%20for%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20playing%20on%20the%20hardwood%2C%20NBA%20players%20are%20used%20to%20a%20pretty%20cushy%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20owner%20of%20the%20Portland%20Trail%20Blazers%2C%20Tom%20Dundon%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20changing%20that%20with%20moves%20that%20echo%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-hardcore-era-employee-changes-att-memo-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehardcore%20grindset%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20increasingly%20popular%20in%20the%20business%20world%2C%20where%20employees%20are%20expected%20to%20do%20more%20with%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20Trail%20Blazers%20are%20a%20professional%20sports%20franchise.%20But%20they've%20recently%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20frugal%20measures%20that%20have%20gotten%20attention%20across%20social%20media.%20Simply%20put%2C%20they're%20pulling%20back%20on%20amenities%20that%20have%20become%20industry%20standard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDundon%2C%20who%20made%20his%20fortune%20in%20subprime%20auto%20loans%2C%20led%20an%20investor%20group%20that%20in%20March%20paid%20%244.25%20billion%20for%20the%20Trail%20Blazers.%20Forbes%20estimates%20that%20Dundon's%20net%20worth%20is%20%242.3%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20decision%20that%20drew%20criticism%20was%20not%20having%20two-way%20players%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20contracts%20allow%20them%20to%20split%20time%20between%20the%20top-level%20NBA%20and%20the%20developmental%20G%20League%20%E2%80%94%20travel%20with%20the%20team%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rosegardenreport.com%2Ftrail-blazers-two-way-players-watching-playoff-run-from-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Rose%20Garden%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20players%20aren't%20expected%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20high-stakes%20games%2C%20but%20are%20still%20considered%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Dundon%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fathletic%2F7213935%2F2026%2F04%2F21%2Fblazers-tom-dundon-nba-owner-expenses-money-cheap%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elate%20hotel%20checkouts%20are%20no%20longer%20allowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20any%20non-players%20or%20coaches.%20According%20to%20The%20Athletic%2C%20this%20concerned%20interim%20head%20coach%20Tiago%20Splitter%2C%20who%20was%20worried%20about%20whether%20the%20team's%20masseuse%20had%20enough%20room%20to%20work%20before%20the%20Blazers'%20opening-round%20game%20of%20the%20NBA%20Play-In%20tournament%2C%20where%20a%20win%20would%20secure%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20NBA%20playoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDundon%20has%20also%20reportedly%20ruffled%20feathers%20with%20Splitter%20by%20interviewing%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20potential%20head%20coaches%20even%20as%20interim%20head%20coach%20led%20the%20franchise%20to%20the%20Play-In%20game%20victory%20and%20thus%20secured%20the%20Blazers'%20first%20NBA%20playoff%20appearance%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20fans%20aren't%20immune%20from%20the%20cost-cutting%20efforts.%20The%20Blazers%20opted%20not%20to%20drape%20fans'%20seats%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D29e1da83efca779e1c6f27c5ed343012050c1572ebcf1ddfcc94bdfe49185982%26postID%3D69ebad7d31845c865e31eb1e%26postSlug%3Dportland-trail-blazers-owner-tom-dundon-cost-cutting-hardcore-2026-4%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.espn.com%252Fnba%252Fstory%252F_%252Fid%252F48542312%252Fblazers-not-furnishing-fans-t-shirts-invites-cash-questions%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efree%20T-shirts%3C%2Fa%3E%20ahead%20of%20a%20playoff%20home%20game%2C%20ESPN%20reported.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20San%20Antonio%20Spurs%2C%20who%20the%20Blazers%20are%20up%20against%20in%20round%20one%2C%20handed%20out%20color-coordinated%20shirts%20to%20their%20fans%20ahead%20of%20Game%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20Mark%20Cuban%2C%20whose%20Dallas%20Mavericks%20were%20known%20for%20their%20perks%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20ballooning%20value%20of%20teams%20has%20drastically%20changed%20the%20equation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Cuban%2C%20the%20former%20owner%20of%20the%20Dallas%20Mavericks%2C%20celebrates%20with%20the%20Larry%20O'Brien%20trophy%20after%20the%20Mavericks%20won%20105-95%20against%20the%20Miami%20Heat%20in%20Game%20Six%20of%20the%202011%20NBA%20Finals.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ebe544367066d7c2970e44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222656%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Cuban%2C%20former%20owner%20of%20the%20Dallas%20Mavericks%2C%20celebrates%20after%20the%20team%20won%20game%20six%20of%20the%202011%20NBA%20Finals.%3Cp%3EMarc%20Serota%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20an%20era%20where%20teams%20cost%20billions%20and%20billions%20of%20dollars%20and%20require%20a%20list%20of%20investors%20and%20even%20private%20equity%2C%20we%20are%20far%20from%20the%20world%20when%20I%20bought%20the%20Mavs%20and%20wrote%20the%20check%20by%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20cover%20the%20losses.%20They%20were%20my%20responsibility.%20With%20investors%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20same%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20said%20the%20pressure%20is%20on%20owners%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20can%20position%20their%20franchises%20successfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20way%20to%20get%20the%20team%20in%20a%20position%20to%20truly%20succeed%20and%20ever%20even%20considering%20paying%20a%20tax%20is%20to%20get%20to%20at%20least%20break%20even%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDundon%20implemented%20similar%20cost-cutting%20changes%20when%20he%20bought%20the%20NHL's%20Carolina%20Hurricanes%20in%202017.%20The%20Hurricanes%20have%20made%20the%20playoffs%20every%20year%20since%202018%20after%20a%20nearly%20decade-long%20drought%20before%20he%20took%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NBA%20isn't%20the%20NHL%2C%20though.%20Dundon's%20actions%20have%20drawn%20so%20much%20attention%20that%20even%20NBA%20Commissioner%20Adam%20Silver%20has%20been%20asked%20about%20the%20cost%20cutting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20starting%20to%20say%20he's%20not%20willing%20to%20spend%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Silver%20recently%20told%20The%20Barstool%20podcast%2C%20%26quot%3BPardon%20my%20Take.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BYou%20gotta%20remember%2C%20this%20is%20a%20guy%20who%20just%20won%20a%20bidding%20war%2C%20call%20it%20%244.5%20billion%20to%20buy%20a%20team%2C%20and%20they're%20calling%20him%20cheap.%20It%20just%20can't%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESilver%20said%20the%20Hurricanes'%20success%20shows%20Dundon%20%26quot%3Bknows%20what%20he's%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20mindset%20is%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I'm%20just%20getting%20to%20know%20him%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20has%20as%20much%20to%20do%20with%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20T-shirts%20or%20wherever%20he's%20saving%20money.%20It's%20a%20mindset%20on%20how%20to%20run%20a%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Silver%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a3b4e74-af1d-4827-9f83-1511dea90e91%5C%22%3EA%20change%20for%20a%20team%20once%20owned%20by%20Microsoft%20cofounder%20Paul%20Allen%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paul%20Allen%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20Portland%20Trail%20Blazers%20looks%20on%20from%20his%20seat%20against%20the%20Golden%20State%20Warriors%20during%20an%20NBA%20basketball%20game%20at%20ORACLE%20Arena%20on%20March%2011%2C%202016%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ebe7663fecbb42897a3f8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaul%20Allen%2C%20the%20late%20former%20owner%20of%20the%20Portland%20Trail%20Blazers%2C%20during%20an%20NBA%20basketball%20game%20in%202016.%3Cp%3EThearon%20W.%20Henderson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20penny-pinching%20sports%20owners%20are%20nothing%20new%2C%20Dundon's%20approach%20stands%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20Paul%20Allen%2C%20the%20legendary%20Microsoft%20cofounder%2C%20who%2C%20during%20his%20tenure%2C%20had%20his%20players'%20cars%20washed%20and%20detailed%20during%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllen%2C%20who%20died%20in%202018%20due%20to%20complications%20of%20non-Hodgkin's%20lymphoma%2C%20passed%20on%20ownership%20to%20his%20sister%2C%20Jody%2C%20who%20helped%20manage%20the%20franchise%20until%20its%20sale%20to%20Dundon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20obituary%2C%20The%20Athletic%20noted%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fathletic%2F592538%2F2018%2F10%2F16%2Ffor-paul-allen-the-trail-blazers-were-more-than-his-team-they-were-his-passion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAllen's%20Trail%20Blazers%20were%20among%20the%20first%20to%20have%20a%20private%20jet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Former%20coach%20Nate%20McMillan%20recalled%20that%20after%20Allen%20hosted%20the%20team%20on%20his%20yacht%2C%20he%20said%20the%20players%20could%20have%20the%20keys%20if%20they%20won%20the%20NBA%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%20the%20team%20could%20cruise%20wherever%20they%20wanted%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20McMillan%20told%20The%20Athletic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20was%20known%20for%20his%20unconventional%20approach%20to%20ownership.%20Cuban's%20approach%20also%20extended%20to%20how%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DczRa0KDyITY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elavished%20the%20Dallas%20Mavericks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20Cuban%20ensured%20that%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20outcome%2C%20the%20Mavericks'%20opponent%20received%20a%20decadent%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20embarrass%20other%20owners%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notoriously%20competitive%20Cuban%20said%20during%20a%202023%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BAll%20The%20Smoke%26quot%3B%20podcast%20cohosted%20by%20former%2C%20longtime%20NBA%20players%20Matt%20Barnes%20and%20Stephen%20Jackson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuys%20we%20would%20trade%20for%20would%20tell%20me%2C%20'We%20just%20went%20from%20the%20outhouse%20to%20the%20penthouse.'%20And%20I'm%20like%2C%20OK%2C%20I%20just%20want%20to%20rub%20it%20in%20a%20little%20bit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Dundon%2C%20Cuban%20said%20their%20new%20owner%20%26quot%3Bknows%20basketball.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20loves%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BHe%20will%20be%20great%20for%20the%20Blazers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportland-trail-blazers-owner-tom-dundon-cost-cutting-hardcore-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777194901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ebc51fa98bc8fdc096e995%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportland-trail-blazers-owner-tom-dundon-cost-cutting-hardcore-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20NBA%20is%20known%20for%20its%20perks.%20New%20Portland%20Trail%20Blazers%20owner%20and%20businessman%20Tom%20Dundon%20is%20testing%20how%20many%20he%20can%20cut.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20quit%20my%20tech%20job%20because%20I%20worried%20that%20AI%20was%20going%20to%20eventually%20replace%20me%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lis%20Cooper%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e8d0ee367066d7c296f837%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221530%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELis%20Cooper%20quit%20their%20job%20as%20a%20data%20analyst%20in%20part%20because%20they%20were%20concerned%20that%20AI%20would%20replace%20them.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lis%20Cooper%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELis%20Cooper%20quit%20their%20job%20as%20a%20data%20analyst%20due%20to%20concerns%20that%20AI%20was%20on%20track%20to%20replace%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECooper%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Australia%2C%20had%20also%20grown%20disillusioned%20with%20the%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20Cooper%20has%20to%20determine%20what's%20next%20for%20their%20career%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20terrifying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELis%20Cooper%2C%2030%2C%20lives%20in%20Melbourne%20and%20recently%20quit%20their%20job%20as%20a%20data%20analyst%20at%20a%20tech%20company%20after%20becoming%20disillusioned%20with%20the%20industry%20and%20growing%20concerned%20that%20AI%20would%20eventually%20replace%20them.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20brevity%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20working%20at%20a%20large%20tech%20company%20doing%20data%20analytics%2C%20which%20I%20enjoyed.%20In%20a%20meeting%2C%20leaders%20were%20sharing%20their%20plans%20for%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years.%20They%20told%20us%20we%C2%A0would%20be%20rebuilding%20our%20data%20warehouse%20to%20optimize%20it%20for%20AI%20data%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20raised%20my%20hand%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20optimizing%20the%20data%20warehouse%20for%20AI%20data%20analysis.%20But%20we%20are%20data%20analysts.%20How%20does%20that%20fit%20in%20with%20our%20jobs%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20we%20would%20be%20doing%20the%20warehouse%20build%20for%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years%20and%20that%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20focus%20on%20data%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20role%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years%20had%20been%20making%20graphs%2C%20and%20the%20company%20was%20saying%20AI%20would%20do%20this%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0that%20it%20would%20spin%20up%20these%20graphs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20around%20in%20dismay%20at%20my%20data-analyst%20colleagues%2C%20who%20I%20think%20fit%20into%20two%20camps%3A%20the%20AI%20true%20believers%20and%20the%20Luddites%2C%20a%20word%20that%20I%20say%20with%20a%20very%20positive%20connotation%2C%20because%20it's%20OK%20to%20be%20skeptical%20of%20automation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20evening%2C%20I%20decided%20that%20I%20probably%20should%20leave%20the%20company.%20Based%20on%20what%20I%20knew%20was%20going%20on%20at%20other%20companies%2C%20I%20knew%20mine%20wasn't%20the%20only%20one%20approaching%20AI%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20my%20finances%2C%20because%20I%20also%20had%20a%20mortgage%20I%20couldn't%20pay%20without%20my%20salary.%20It%20was%20about%20three%20months%20between%20that%20meeting%20and%20my%20resignation%20because%20I%20had%20to%20sell%20my%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20decision%20to%20leave%20wasn't%20only%20related%20to%20AI.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI've%20lost%20faith%20in%20the%20industry%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20particularly%20with%20people%20becoming%20overly%20reliant%20on%20technology%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flarry-fink-blackrock-ceo-davos-critiques-capitalism-ai-wealth-inequality-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewealth%20inequality%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20these%20companies%20can%20exacerbate.%20I'm%20also%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20environmental%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-development-true-cost-environmental-impact-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimpact%20of%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20was%20the%20kicker%20for%20me.%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20this%20is%20all%20going%20to%20end%20anyway.%20They're%20going%20to%20be%20laying%20us%20off.%20And%20if%20I'm%20laid%20off%2C%20I%20can't%20pay%20my%20mortgage%20immediately%2C%20so%20I%20may%20as%20well%20sort%20out%20the%20mortgage%20thing%20and%20then%20figure%20out%20the%20next%20step%20a%20bit%20earlier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8781f49-7e95-4e1c-af57-cc308ef4be8e%5C%22%3EI%20want%20to%20be%20more%20analog%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20if%20I%20did%20this%2C%20I%20likely%20would%20not%20get%20another%20tech%20role%20because%20the%20job%20market%20is%20not%20what%20it%20was%20when%20I%20started%20about%2010%20years%20ago.%20So%20that%20made%20leaving%20a%20really%20scary%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20there's%20a%20tech%20role%20out%20there%20for%20me%20at%20a%20nonprofit%20or%20at%20some%20company%20that%20is%20trying%20to%20make%20the%20world%20better%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20stay%20at%20that%20company%20and%20try%20to%20look%20for%20something.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20needs%20to%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20was%20so%20easy%20to%20leave%20a%20company%20and%20find%20a%20role.%20My%20colleagues%20and%20I%20would%20have%20companies%20messaging%20us%20all%20the%20time%2C%20asking%20to%20poach%20us.%20It%20is%20not%20like%20that%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20going%20to%20be%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20at%20a%20coffee%20shop%20or%20a%20restaurant.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20more%20analog.%20I%20want%20to%20see%20people%20face%20to%20face%2C%20have%20chats%2C%20be%20in%20the%20community%2C%20or%20maybe%20do%20hairdressing%20%E2%80%94%20something%20with%20my%20hands.%20I'm%20also%20thinking%20about%20teaching%20and%20helping%20the%20next%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20lots%20of%20things%20I%20could%20do.%20I'm%20actually%20kind%20of%20struggling%20with%20the%20choices%20because%20I%20have%20so%20many%20possibilities%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20It's%20kind%20of%20terrifying.%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%2017%20again%2C%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20I%20want%20to%20do%20after%20high%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20reach%20out%20to%20me%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI've%20got%20this%20company%20where%20we're%20trying%20to%20do%20ethical%20AI.%26quot%3B%20I%20have%20no%20doubt%20that%20there%20may%20be%20job%20offers%20around%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20make%20the%20world%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20career%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atparadis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etparadis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-analyst-quit-job-over-concerns-ai-would-replace-them-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777194841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e8d0ee367066d7c296f837%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-analyst-quit-job-over-concerns-ai-would-replace-them-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20data%20analyst%20quit%20their%20tech%20job%20over%20concerns%20that%20AI%20would%20replace%20them%20and%20about%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20industry%20in%20general.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinside