-shield-faces-budget-squeeze-despite-pentagon-push%2Famp_articleshow%2F130529115.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20took%20a%20paid%20apprenticeship%20instead%20of%20going%20to%20college.%20I'll%20make%20six%20figures%20within%205%20years%20%E2%80%94%20the%20stability%20I%20feel%20is%20incredible.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smiling%20person%20in%20a%20black%20Nike%20polo%20leans%20against%20a%20railing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20leafy%20ivy-covered%20wall.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69eb8976367066d7c29709ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChris%20Rocha%20skipped%20college%20to%20become%20a%20pipe%20fitter.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Chris%20Rocha%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E18-year-old%20Chris%20Rocha%20chose%20a%205-year%20pipe-fitting%20apprenticeship%20over%20college.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERocha%20earns%20nearly%20%2460%2C000%20now%20and%20is%20on%20track%20to%20make%20six%20figures%20when%20his%20apprenticeship%20is%20over.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20thinks%20the%20job%20is%20AI-proof%20and%20values%20the%20stability%20despite%20missing%20college's%20social%20aspect.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Chris%20Rocha%2C%20an%2018-year-old%20pipe%20fitting%20apprentice%20for%20Local%20533%2C%20based%20in%20Kansas%20City.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20junior%20year%20of%20high%20school%2C%20I%20decided%20I%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhvac-technician-skipped-college-doesnt-worry-about-ai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eskip%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20become%20a%20pipe%20fitter.%20Then%2C%20last%20summer%2C%20right%20after%20my%2018th%20birthday%2C%20I%20applied%20to%20my%20local%20union%2C%20Local%20533%2C%20for%20a%20pipe-fitting%20apprenticeship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20I%20would've%20gone%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-not-happening-borrowers-prepare-debt-repayment-treasury-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudent%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20I%20chose%20college.%20Meanwhile%2C%20with%20my%20apprenticeship%2C%20I'm%20getting%20paid%20to%20work%20and%20go%20to%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20finish%20my%20five-year%20program%2C%20I'm%20on%20track%20to%20make%20six%20figures%20right%20away.%20I%20think%20it's%20hard%20not%20to%20feel%20a%20little%20nervous%20when%20it's%20not%20the%20normal%20career%20path%2C%20but%20the%20stability%20I%20feel%20is%20incredible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b4d5f10-9428-4538-9326-a9fea8da5117%5C%22%3EI%20grew%20up%20around%20the%20trades%20and%20realized%20college%20wasn't%20for%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20helping%20out%20in%20the%20office%20at%20my%20mom's%20construction%20company%2C%20probably%20at%2015%20or%2016.%20It%20was%20small%20stuff%3A%20helping%20with%20paperwork%20and%20sorting%20things%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20shop%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20I%20considered%20pursuing%20construction%20science%20or%20engineering%20in%20school.%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20see%20which%20college%20I%20could%20play%20baseball%20at.%20Then%2C%20junior%20year%20came%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20see%20myself%20going%20anywhere%20for%20baseball.%20My%20grandfather%20was%20also%20a%20pipe%20fitter%2C%20so%20I%20had%20good%20background%20knowledge%20on%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20all%20of%20that%2C%20plus%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-student-loan-debt-repayment-struggle-warning-for-federal-borrowers-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudent%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20would've%20had%20to%20take%20on%2C%20it%20didn't%20feel%20like%20a%20hard%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9514589-5599-406c-a1e7-1b6b288443a8%5C%22%3EAt%2018%2C%20I%20jumped%20straight%20into%20a%20paid%20apprenticeship%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20apply%20to%20the%20union%20until%20I%20turned%2018.%20Once%20I%20turned%2018%20last%20July%2C%20I%20went%20to%20my%20union%20and%20applied%20for%20my%20letter%20of%20eligibility%20with%20my%20high%20school%20diploma%2C%20birth%20certificate%2C%20and%20transcript.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20applied%20and%20received%20my%20letter%20of%20eligibility%2C%20I%20had%20to%20get%20a%20job%20with%20a%20contractor%20before%20I%20could%20join%20the%20union.%20I%20started%20working%20at%20my%20mom's%20company%20to%20officially%20join%20the%20union%20and%20start%20my%20apprenticeship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20there%20are%20about%20800%20applicants%20on%20file%20who%20are%20eligible%20for%20the%20apprenticeship%20program%20spots%20each%20year.%20The%20program%20is%20on%20a%20rolling%20basis%2C%20but%20if%20you%20miss%20the%20summer%20cutoff%20date%2C%20you%20can't%20start%20classes%20until%20the%20following%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ead20dbe-2ad7-4c22-ab80-7ee54a339137%5C%22%3EI%20work%20full-time%20and%20go%20to%20class%20twice%20a%20week%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20starting%20at%206%20a.m.%20every%20day.%20I%20have%20class%20for%20my%20apprenticeship%20two%20nights%20a%20week.%20My%20first%20year%20includes%20a%20math%2C%20science%2C%20and%20skills%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20have%20class%2C%20I%20leave%20work%20early%20around%203%20p.m.%20or%203%3A30%20p.m.%20to%20get%20ready%20and%20drive%20to%20the%20union%20for%20school.%20If%20not%2C%20I'm%20done%20with%20work%20at%204%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20good%20number%20of%20us%20in%20the%20program%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-pivot-college-degrees-work-blue-collar-jobs-trades-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estraight%20out%20of%20high%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20there%20are%20also%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20with%20significant%20experience%20who%20just%20want%20to%20get%20into%20the%20union.%20Some%20are%20in%20their%2030s%20and%20up%2C%20but%20the%20majority%20are%20a%20few%20years%20out%20of%20high%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22172f257d-fc53-46a8-8e0d-7de26f44dd5f%5C%22%3EMy%20earned%20income%20is%20nearly%20%2460K%20already%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20make%20%2428.76%20an%20hour%2C%20working%2040%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20little%20bit%20less%20than%20%2460%2C000%20a%20year%20right%20out%20of%20high%20school.%20Every%20year%2C%20I'll%20get%20a%20raise%20as%20I%20move%20through%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20I%20make%20around%2050%25%20of%20what%20I%20am%20supposed%20to%20make%20by%20the%20time%20I%20graduate%20from%20my%20apprenticeship.%20My%20first%20year%2C%20I'll%20get%20a%205%25%20raise%2C%20and%20then%2010%25%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20until%20I%20reach%20the%20full%20scale.%20I%20could%20be%20making%20around%20%24115%2C000%20when%20I%20finish%20the%20apprenticeship%20at%2023%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funion-pipe-fitter-earns-6-figures-advice-get-into-trades-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebecome%20a%20journeyman%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20provides%20health%20and%20welfare%20benefits%20and%20a%20vacation%20fund.%20I%20also%20have%20dental%20insurance%20and%20a%20standard%20health%20insurance%20plan%20through%20the%20union.%20They%20can%20also%20get%20me%20raises%20through%20their%20contract%20with%20the%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2278ee87ee-ebfa-4778-b39b-846231223723%5C%22%3EThe%20job%20is%20hands-on%20and%20super%20unpredictable%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20also%20AI-proof%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20the%20problem-solving%20aspect%20of%20pipe%20fitting%3B%20if%20something%20breaks%2C%20how%20do%20we%20fix%20it%2C%20how%20do%20we%20get%20this%20one%20piece%20to%20fit%2C%20etc.%20It's%20a%20lot%20of%20almost-maintenance-like%20work%2C%20but%20I%20really%20like%20working%20with%20my%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20experience%20has%20been%20seeing%20all%20the%20different%20sites.%20I%20could%20be%20working%20in%20manufacturing%20plants%20or%20new%20builds.%20It's%20been%20really%20cool%20to%20see%20how%20different%20one%20job%20can%20be%20from%20the%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hours%20can%20sometimes%20be%20tough%20and%20long%2C%20and%20the%20job%20can%20take%20a%20toll%20on%20my%20body%2C%20but%20I'm%20also%20learning%20so%20much%20on%20those%20days.%20Another%20thing%20is%20that%20this%20career%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-collar-work-isnt-safe-ai-trade-tech-ceo-says-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20AI-proof%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20many%20other%20jobs%20right%20now.%20AI%20can't%20be%20working%20hands-on%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22881082ee-d006-47f4-aaca-dd6c30fc6459%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20regret%20skipping%20college%2C%20but%20sometimes%20I%20miss%20the%20social%20life%20it%20could%20provide%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20made%20friends%20through%20my%20program%20by%20meeting%20people%20in%20class%20and%20out%20in%20the%20field.%20One%20of%20my%20classes%20includes%20the%20entire%20apprenticeship%20group.%20I%20can%20go%20to%20class%20and%20meet%20someone%20I've%20never%20seen%20before%2C%20even%20though%20I've%20had%20class%20with%20them%20for%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20my%20friends%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgraduating-class-college-cheating-chatgpt-ai-jobs-hiring-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewent%20off%20to%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20high%20school.%20One%20or%20two%20stayed%20local%20for%20school%2C%20but%20not%20many%20stayed%20around.%20I%20don't%20feel%20regret%20over%20my%20decision%2C%20but%20there%20have%20been%20times%20when%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20missing%20out%20on%20the%20social%20aspect%20of%20college%2C%20especially%20when%20I'm%20not%20working%20on%20so