0robot%20built%20by%20Foundation%2C%20was%20sent%20to%20Ukraine%20for%20a%20pilot%20demonstration%20of%20a%20supply%20pickup%20scenario.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Foundation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFoundation%20is%20a%20startup%20building%20general-purpose%20humanoid%20robots.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETwo%20of%20Foundation's%20robots%20were%20sent%20to%20Ukraine%20for%20a%20demo%20of%20a%20supply%20transport%20scenario.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Sankaet%20Pathak%20said%20he%20sees%20humanoids%20becoming%20valuable%20for%20precision%20operations%20in%20warfare.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhumanoid-robot-companies-us-tesla-figure-1x-agility-apptronik-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHumanoid%20robots%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20flesh-and-blood%20soldiers%20could%20one%20day%20take%20on%20some%20of%20the%20most%20dangerous%20jobs%20in%20war%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20startup%20is%20already%20testing%20that%20idea%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESankaet%20Pathak%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Foundation%2C%20said%20there's%20a%20%26quot%3Bmoral%20imperative%26quot%3B%20to%20put%20humanoid%20robots%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20rather%20than%20in%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsunday-robotics-home-robot-training-hands-loading-dishwasher-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeople's%20kitchens%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20all%20of%20this%20stuff%20around%20home%20use%20was%20kind%20of%20stupid%2C%26quot%3B%20Pathak%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20people%20can%20make%20the%20coffee%20and%20fold%20their%20laundry.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'We%20need%20to%20do%20something%20else.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvancements%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-us-top-allies-fall-behind-in-drone-defense-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrone%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20robotics%20are%20now%20central%20to%20the%20arsenal%20of%20modern%20warfare%2C%20enabling%20precision%20attacks%20at%20scale%20and%20at%20lower%20cost%3B%20however%2C%20that%20capability%20hasn't%20always%20translated%20into%20clean%2C%20risk-free%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20age%20of%20smart%20weapons%20and%20AI-enabled%2C%20autonomous%20systems%2C%20modern%20warfare%20still%20carries%20a%20high%20risk%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-drone-strike-kills-10-afghan-civilians-not-isolated-incident-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecivilian%20casualties%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20in%20dense%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-gaza-urban-warfare-tactics-lessons-nato-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eurban%20environments%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222934%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20robot%20packs%20boxes%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ed36b4367066d7c297105c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221541%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFoundation%20wants%20to%20deploy%20its%20robots%20for%20reconnaissance%20and%20supply%20logistics.%3Cp%3EFoundation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPathak%20said%20the%20current%20approach%20to%20war%20is%20often%20%26quot%3Bbrute%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20either%20risking%20soldiers'%20lives%20or%20destroying%20a%20building%20to%20eliminate%20a%20single%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20believes%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20humanoids%20could%20execute%20%26quot%3Bsurgical%26quot%3B%20operations%2C%20such%20as%20extracting%20a%20target.%20Near-term%2C%20they%20could%20support%20military%20operations%20such%20as%20reconnaissance%20and%20logistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFoundation%20said%20it%20recently%20conducted%20a%20test%20that%20could%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20those%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20the%20startup%20sent%20two%20of%20its%20Phantom%20robots%20to%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20Ukraine%20for%20a%20closed%20pilot%20demonstration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20hear%20bombs%20go%20off.%20You%20can%20hear%20electricity%20get%20cut.%20You're%20actively%20in%20a%20warzone%2C%26quot%3B%20Pathak%20said%20of%20Foundation's%20visit%20to%20the%20country%2C%20which%20for%20years%20has%20been%20fighting%20off%20a%20Russian%20invasion.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20places%20are%20a%20battlefield%20as%20soon%20as%20you%20start%20going%20out%20of%20Kyiv.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20said%20the%20Phantom%20test%20solely%20focused%20on%20%26quot%3Bsupply%20pickup%26quot%3B%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20bipedal%20robots%20can%20effectively%20%26quot%3Bcarry%20supplies%20from%20outside%20to%20inside%20and%20avoid%20a%20soldier%20getting%20shot%20at.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20interest%20based%20on%20what%20has%20been%20communicated%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20company%2C%20Pathak%20said.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20Foundation%20said%20the%20startup%20has%20also%20secured%20a%20%2424%20million%20contract%20with%20the%20Pentagon.%20Eric%20Trump%2C%20the%20president's%20son%2C%20was%20appointed%20chief%20strategy%20advisor%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e0ce9b3-9b03-4e5f-8bf5-fd5eda54c136%5C%22%3EHumanoid%20troops%20aren't%20ready%20for%20deployment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPathak%20said%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20%26quot%3Boverstate%26quot%3B%20the%20Ukraine%20pilot.%20A%20large%20gap%20still%20exists%20between%20a%20humanoid%20that%20can%20slowly%20clean%20a%20test%20kitchen%20and%20one%20that%20can%20use%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ean%20M4%20carbine%20in%20a%20battlefield%20firefight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBattery%20life%20and%20durability%20are%20among%20the%20constraints.%20Pathak%20said%20robot%20soldiers%20need%20longer%20battery%20life%20and%20must%20withstand%20water%2C%20dust%2C%20and%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221421%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Phantom%2C%20humanoid%20robot.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ebe59e367066d7c2970e4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPathak%20said%20the%20test%20demonstrated%20that%20bipedal%20robots%20can%20be%20used%20for%20certain%20applications.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Foundation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EReliable%20manipulation%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ability%20for%20a%20robot%20to%20pick%20up%20an%20item%20and%20do%20something%20with%20it%2C%20like%20pulling%20the%20trigger%20on%20a%20rifle%20%E2%80%94%20also%20remains%20a%20major%20technological%20bottleneck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20the%20big%20engineering%20hurdle%20is%20how%20do%20you%20build%20a%20highly-dextrous%20hand%20that%20is%20reliable%2C%20easier%20to%20manufacture%2C%20isn't%20too%20massive%2C%20and%20isn't%20too%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Pathak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20offered%20ambitious%20predictions%20for%20overcoming%20these%20challenges%2C%20saying%20that%20key%20engineering%20hurdles%20could%20be%20solved%20within%20a%20few%20years%20and%20that%20humanoid%20robots%20could%20carry%20out%20complex%20missions%2C%20such%20as%20target%20extraction%2C%20within%20five%20to%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20technical%20questions%2C%20ethical%20dilemmas%20surrounding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-ai-military-use-dario-amodei-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eautonomous%20weaponry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20concerns%20of%20accountability%20when%20humans%20are%20no%20longer%20in%20the%20loop%2C%20are%20also%20a%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPathak%20said%20that%20while%20there%20isn't%20a%20simple%20line%20that%20can%20be%20drawn%20around%20autonomy%2C%20in%20ordinary%20circumstances%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20probably%20want%20a%20human%20in%20the%20loop%20before%20any%20kind%20of%20kill%20action%20is%20invoked.%26quot%3B%20Many%20Western%20militaries%20have%20made%20that%20a%20priority%20amid%20rapid%20technological%20advances%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20autonomous%20systems%2C%20though%20the%20extent%20remains%20an%20active%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20if%20you%20actually%20need%20to%20shoot%20a%20gun%2C%20you%20need%20a%20human%20to%20really%20sign%20off%2C%20which%20is%20what%20happens%20with%20drones%20today%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20there%20are%20exceptions%20to%20those%20cases%20as%20well%2C%20like%20an%20anti-drone%20gun%20or%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-iron-dome-missile-defense-system-history-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIron%20Dome%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Those%2C%20you%20cannot%20wait%20for%20human%20reaction%20times%20because%20the%20alternative%20is%20100%25%20certainty%20of%20fatality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20industry%20at%20large%20pushes%20robotics%20and%20autonomous%20weapons%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20national%20security.%20Anduril%20cofounder%20Palmer%20Luckey%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20that%20the%20United%20States%20needs%20to%20be%20ahead%20of%20China%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalmer-luckey-ai-weapons-pandoras-box-china-arms-race-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20top%20US%20admiral%20in%20the%20Pacific%20said%20this%20week%20that%20America's%20AI%20technology%20lead%20over%20China%20is%20only%20six%20months%20to%20a%20year%20at%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20other%20companies%2C%20Foundation%20has%20been%20particularly%20outspoken%20on%20using%20humanoids%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCourage%20comes%20in%20limited%20supply%2C%26quot%3B%20Pathak%20said%2C%20while%20arguing%20that%20China%20is%20not%20having%20the%20same%20debate%20over%20military%20humanoids%20and%20that%20the%20US%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20their%20allies%20need%20to%20be%20on%20alert.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20build%20a%20utopia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20defend%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffoundation-humanoid-robot-soldier-ukraine-testing-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777191061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ebc292a98bc8fdc096e975%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffoundation-humanoid-robot-soldier-ukraine-testing-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Foundation%20sent%20humanoid%20robots%20to%20Ukraine%20for%20a%20demonstration.%20CEO%20Sankaet%20Pathak%20said%20that%20in%205%20to%2010%20years%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20extract%20targets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Are%20Trump%2C%20Netanyahu%20in%20sync%3F%20How%20US%20and%20Israel%20are%20fighting%20different%20wars%20on%20same%20battlefield%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777190863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130528529%2Cimgsize-885987.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fare-trump-netanyahu-in-sync-how-us-and-israel-are-fighting-different-wars-on-same-battlefield%2Farticleshow%2F130528098.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20two-month%20conflict%20with%20Iran%20escalates%2C%20cracks%20are%20appearing%20in%20the%20US-Israel%20alliance.%20While%20both%20nations%20initially%20targeted%20Tehran%2C%20their%20post-strike%20objectives%20diverge%2C%20with%20Washington%20seeking%20negotiation%20and%20Jerusalem%20aiming%20for%20regime%20change.%20This%20fundamental%20difference%2C%20exacerbated%20by%20past%20events%20and%20differing%20pressures%2C%20raises%20questions%20about%20their%20lon