k-donald-trump-rally-butler-pennsylvania-assassination-attempt-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eparticularly%20vocal%20Trump%20backer%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-butler-pennsylvania-rally-secret-service-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJuly%202024%20assassination%20attempt%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20Trump%20campaign%20rally%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania.%20In%202025%2C%20the%20two%20hit%20a%20relationship%20rough%20patch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musks-relationship-over-tesla-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eand%20traded%20some%20barbs%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-donald-trump-feud-relationship-timeline-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20cordial%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20public%20events%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDana%20White%2C%20UFC%20CEO%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dana%20White%20attends%20the%202026%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%20at%20Washington%20Hilton%20on%20April%2025%2C%202026%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ed9292a98bc8fdc096ed84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222501%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUFC%20CEO%20Dana%20White%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner.%3Cp%3EPaul%20Morigi%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20was%20a%20guest%20at%20the%20dinner%20and%20was%20in%20the%20room%20when%20chaos%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20fucking%20awesome.%20I%20literally%20took%20every%20minute%20of%20it%20in.%20It%20was%20a%20pretty%20crazy%2C%20unique%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20was%20seen%20saying%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20X%20by%20MMAJunkie%2C%20part%20of%20USA%20Today's%20sports%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMark%20Thompson%2C%20chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20CNN%20Worldwide%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Thompson%2C%20Chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20CNN%20Worldwide%20attends%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery's%202025%20Upfront%20arrivals%20at%20The%20Theater%20at%20Madison%20Square%20Garden%20on%20May%2014%2C%202025%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ed960d367066d7c29710f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Thompson%2C%20Chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20CNN%20Worldwide%3Cp%3EDimitrios%20Kambouris%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThompson%20sent%20a%20memo%20to%20all%20CNN%20staffers%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20according%20to%20screenshots%20of%20the%20memo%20posted%20to%20X%20by%20Brian%20Stelter%2C%20the%20network's%20chief%20media%20analyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThompson%20highlighted%20the%20CNN%20team's%20real-time%20response%20and%20on-the-ground%20reporting%20as%20the%20shooting%20unfolded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20this%20was%20a%20frightening%20and%20disruptive%20situation%20for%20those%20in%20the%20room%2C%20and%20for%20your%20colleagues%20and%20loved%20ones%20watching%20live%20on%20CNN.%20Moments%20like%20this%20can%20stay%20with%20you%20in%20ways%20that%20aren't%20necessarily%20immediate%20or%20obvious%2C%26quot%3B%20Thompson%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20take%20care%20of%20yourselves%20and%20one%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELuther%20Lowe%2C%20head%20of%20public%20policy%20at%20Y%20Combinator%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Weijia%20Jiang%20and%20Travis%20Luther%20Lowe%20attend%20the%202026%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%20at%20Washington%20Hilton%20on%20April%2025%2C%202026%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ed93b3a98bc8fdc096ed88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222501%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJournalist%20Weijia%20Jiang%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Luther%20Lowe%2C%20head%20of%20public%20policy%20at%20Y%20Combinator.%3Cp%3EPaul%20Morigi%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELowe%20is%20married%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcbs-weijia-jiang-white-house-correspondents-dinner-shooting-trump-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWeijia%20Jiang%2C%20the%20CBS%20journalist%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20chairs%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Association.%20Jiang%20got%20her%20share%20of%20accolades%20from%20media%20peers%20and%20viewers%20alike%20for%20her%20poise%20under%20pressure%20%E2%80%94%20she%20was%20onstage%20next%20to%20Trump%20during%20the%20shooting%2C%20and%20took%20a%20front-row%20seat%20in%20the%20briefing%20room%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20proud%20of%20%40weijia.%20She%20was%20on%20the%20stage%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20ago%20presiding%20over%20the%20abrupt%20end%20of%20the%20dinner%20and%20now%20she's%20in%20the%20front%20row%20of%20the%20White%20House%20briefing%20room%20waiting%20to%20for%20the%20President%20to%20speak%2C%26quot%3B%20Lowe%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETarek%20Mansour%20and%20Luana%20Lopes%20Lara%2C%20cofounders%20of%20Kalshi%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tarek%20Mansour%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Kalshi%2C%20at%20the%20Semafor%20World%20Economy%20Summit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69eda088367066d7c297110a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETarek%20Mansour%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Kalshi.%3Cp%3EIMF%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cofounders%20of%20the%20popular%20predictions%20market%20attended%20the%20event%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20Luana%20and%20I's%20first%20White%20House%20Correspondents%20Dinner.%20The%20moment%20was%20scary%2C%20but%20the%20dinner%20until%20then%20was%20a%20great%20gathering%20of%20people%20from%20all%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20Mansour%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGrateful%20for%20law%20enforcement%20and%20that%20the%20President%20and%20everyone%20is%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20Mansour%20said%2C%20giving%20a%20shoutout%20to%20CBS's%20Jiang%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELara%20thanked%20Mansour%20on%20X%20for%20pulling%20her%20under%20the%20table%20to%20keep%20her%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20co-founder%20isn't%20protecting%20you%20in%20a%20shooting%20situation%2C%20find%20another%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBilal%20Zuberi%2C%20founder%20of%20VC%20firm%20Red%20Glass%20Ventures%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPretty%20scary%20that%20our%20most%20important%20leaders%20of%20the%20government%20were%20at%20risk%20today.%20President%20Trump%2C%20Vice%20President%20Pence%2C%20and%20House%20Speaker%20Johnson%20were%20all%20in%20that%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuberi%20wrote%20on%20X.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20multiple%20attacks%20against%20our%20president%20to%20attacks%20against%20politicians%20around%20the%20country%2C%20to%20attacks%20on%20politicians%20and%20leadership%20around%20the%20world%20-%20these%20are%20abhorrent%2C%20and%20people%20everywhere%20should%20vehemently%20oppose%20and%20condemn%20them!%26quot%3B%20the%20tech%20investor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-leaders-reactions-white-house-correspondents-dinner-shooting-donald-trump-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777179950000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ed97aea98bc8fdc096ed9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-leaders-reactions-white-house-correspondents-dinner-shooting-donald-trump-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Here's%2