Cbr%3Eor%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3Bwe%20still%20need%20to%20looksmaxx%20our%20frontend%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3ECosgrove%20is%20correct.%20There%20are%20also%20other%20uses%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B-maxx%26quot%3B%20suffix.%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-reaction-chinamaxxing-trend-america-rednote-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20term%20%26quot%3BChinamaxxing%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20%26quot%3B-maxxing%26quot%3B%20describes%20going%20full-tilt%20into%20Asian-inspired%20lifestyle%20choices%20like%20practicing%20tai%20chi%20at%20dawn%20and%20drinking%20hot%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20X%20user%20weighed%20in%20on%20Cosgrove's%20explanation%2C%20venturing%20that%20%26quot%3B'Looksmog'%20doesn't%20exist%20you%20just%20say%20'mog.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'lookmogged'%20maybe%20be%20needlessly%20repetitive%20in%20isolation%20but%20it%20provides%20useful%20context%20given%20the%20'IQmog'%20that%20appears%20later%20in%20the%20sentence%2C%26quot%3B%20Cosgrove%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20Sam%20%E2%80%94%20don't%20feel%20bad.%20Lots%20of%20Gen%20Alpha%20internet%20slang%20is%20nearly%20incomprehensible%20to%20us%20millennials.%20Who%20among%20us%20did%20not%20at%20one%20point%20ask%20a%20friend%20or%20colleague%20what%20the%20%26quot%3Byouth%26quot%3B%20mean%20when%20they're%20out%20here%20talking%20about%20%26quot%3Bskibidi%20toilet%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHappy%20weekend%2C%20Silicon%20Valley.%20Now%20let's%20get%20back%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-internet-slang-millennial-moment-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777177587000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ed79ad3fecbb42897a41e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2