ijia%20Jiang%20gets%20props%20for%20poise%20under%20pressure%20after%20press%20dinner%20shooting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227824%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20CBS%20News%20senior%20White%20House%20correspondent%20Weijia%20Jiang%20speak%20as%20they%20attend%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20dinner%20at%20the%20Washington%20Hilton%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20on%20April%2025%2C%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ed8858367066d7c29710c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224906%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECBS's%20Weijia%20Jiang%20is%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Association.%3Cp%3EMandel%20NGAN%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECBS%20senior%20correspondent%20Weijia%20Jiang%20is%20getting%20accolades%20for%20her%20cool%20composure%20on%20Saturday%20night.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJiang%20was%20seated%20next%20to%20Trump%20when%20gunshots%20were%20heard%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20was%20later%20seen%20in%20the%20front%20row%20of%20the%20White%20House%20briefing%20room%2C%20back%20at%20the%20reporting%20grind.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECBS's%20Weijia%20Jiang%20is%20receiving%20praise%20for%20her%20poise%20under%20pressure%20during%20the%20shooting%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20network's%20senior%20White%20House%20correspondent%20is%20the%20president%20of%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Association%2C%20which%20hosts%20the%20annual%20dinner.%20She%20was%20seated%20next%20to%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20onstage%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-evacuated-from-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebedlam%20broke%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Washington%20Hilton%20ballroom%2C%20after%20gunshots%20were%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJiang%20later%20took%20a%20front-row%20seat%20in%20the%20briefing%20room%20and%20asked%20the%20first%20question%20when%20Trump%20took%20questions%20from%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20to%20the%20WH%20with%20President%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20preparing%20for%20a%20press%20conference%20to%20brief%20reporters%2C%26quot%3B%20Jiang%20posted%20on%20X%20before%20the%20briefing.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20to%20have%20more%20answers%20soon.%20A%20few%20of%20us%20are%20waiting%20in%20the%20briefing%20room.%20Thank%20God%20he%2C%20the%20First%20Lady%2C%20and%20everyone%20who%20was%20attending%20the%20WHCD%20was%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20badass%20went%20from%20running%20the%20dinner%20to%20leading%20the%20questions%20from%20the%20briefing%20room.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fweijia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40weijia%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%20are%20just%20the%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20Kristin%20Brown%2C%20the%20White%20House%20producer%20for%20CBS%20News%2C%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20phoning%20into%20CBS%20special%20coverage%20as%20she%20went%20from%20the%20ballroom%20to%20the%20briefing%20room!%26quot%3B%20Oklahoma%20State%20University%20media%20professor%20Dylan%20McLemore%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcLemore%20had%20earlier%20posted%20about%20watching%20Jiang%20%26quot%3Breporting%20by%20phone%20from%20the%20scene%2C%20which%20may%20explain%20why%20CBS%20is%20giving%20coverage%20an%20extended%20network%20window%20compared%20to%20their%20peers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20journalists%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20appeared%20to%20have%20come%20straight%20from%20the%20dinner%2C%20clad%20in%20black%20tie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbsolutely%20baller%20moment%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fhashtag%2FWHCD%3Fsrc%3Dhashtag_click%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23WHCD%3C%2Fa%3E%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fweijia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40Weijia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dressed%20to%20the%20nines%2C%20poised%20at%20a%20godlevel%2C%20asking%20first%20question%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FPOTUS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40POTUS%20%3C%2Fa%3Eafter%20shooting%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20Florida%20Politics%20publisher%20and%20editor%20Peter%20Schorsch%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJiang%20earned%20the%20praise%20online%20for%20her%20remarkable%20composure%2C%20a%20steadiness%20that%20became%20especially%20striking%20given%20how%20quickly%20the%20evening%20descended%20into%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20after%208%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20shortly%20after%20Trump%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20first%20time%20as%20US%20president%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%2C%20an%20individual%20breached%20the%20main%20doors%20of%20the%20event.%20In%20a%20security%20video%2C%20posted%20by%20Trump%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20officers%20in%20the%20video%20could%20be%20seen%20trying%20to%20grab%20the%20man%2C%20then%20drawing%20their%20weapons%20and%20pointing%20their%20guns%20at%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%2C%20shouting%20at%20the%20front%20of%20the%20stage%20gave%20way%20to%20pushing%20and%20chaos%20as%20people%20started%20running%2C%20guests%20threw%20themselves%20to%20the%20floor%2C%20and%20hid%20under%20tables%2C%20according%20to%20Tim%20R%C3%B6hn%2C%20the%20senior%20editor%20of%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20event.%20Business%20Insider%20is%20part%20of%20the%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Secret%20Service%20ushered%20Trump%20and%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20off%20the%20stage%2C%20heavily%20armed%20officers%20emerged%20from%20behind%20the%20curtains%20onstage%20and%20pointed%20their%20rifles%20at%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20short%20time%20afterward%2C%20video%20streams%20from%20inside%20the%20event%20room%20showed%20a%20lull%20as%20attendees%20appeared%20confused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20Jiang%20took%20the%20stage%20to%20say%20the%20night's%20programming%20would%20continue.%20She%20later%20addressed%20the%20crowd%20again%2C%20saying%20law%20enforcement%20had%20requested%20that%20everyone%20leave%20the%20premises%20%26quot%3Bconsistent%20with%20protocol%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20Trump%20would%20hold%20a%20press%20conference%20shortly%2C%20addressing%20the%20night's%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20she%20appeared%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJiang's%20swift%20return%20to%20reporting%20became%20a%20striking%20visual%20of%20the%20night%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reminder%20that%20in%20Washington%2C%20even%20the%20most%20choreographed%20events%20can%2C%20without%20warning%2C%20turn%20into%20breaking%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcbs-weijia-jiang-white-house-correspondents-dinner-shooting-trump-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777176227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ed8990a98bc8fdc096ed5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcbs-weijia-jiang-white-house-correspondents-dinner-shooting-trump-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CBS's%20Weijia%20Jiang%20is%20getting%20praise%20for%20her%20poise%20under%20pressure%20during%20and%20after%20the%20shooting%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cteh%40businessinsider.com%20(Cheryl%20Teh%2CKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%20shows%20moment%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20evacuated%20from%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Video%20shows%20moment%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20evacuated%20from%20t