confirmed%20one%20individual%20was%20in%20custody%20following%20a%20%26quot%3Bshooting%20incident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAttendees%20of%20the%20event%20reported%20hearing%20loud%20booms%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bcommotion%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20room.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20evacuated%20from%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%20following%20what%20the%20Secret%20Service%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bshooting%20incident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20individual%20was%20in%20custody%20following%20the%20incident%2C%20but%20the%20%26quot%3Bcondition%20of%20those%20involved%20is%20not%20yet%20known%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20by%20the%20Secret%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20after%208%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20shortly%20after%20Trump%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20first%20time%20as%20US%20president%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%20and%20taken%20his%20seat%20onstage%2C%20there%20was%20suddenly%20shouting%20in%20front%20of%20the%20stage%2C%20according%20to%20Tim%20R%C3%B6hn%2C%20Senior%20Editor%20of%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20event.%20Business%20Insider%20is%20part%20of%20the%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ER%C3%B6hn%20reported%20that%20pushing%20and%20chaos%20broke%20out%2C%20people%20started%20running%2C%20guests%20threw%20themselves%20to%20the%20floor%2C%20and%20hid%20under%20tables.%20From%20behind%20the%20curtains%20on%20stage%2C%20heavily%20armed%20officers%20emerged%20and%20pointed%20their%20rifles%20at%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuite%20an%20evening%20in%20D.C.%20Secret%20Service%20and%20Law%20Enforcement%20did%20a%20fantastic%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20after%20the%20incident.%20%26quot%3BThey%20acted%20quickly%20and%20bravely.%20The%20shooter%20has%20been%20apprehended%2C%20and%20I%20have%20recommended%20that%20we%20%26quot%3BLET%20THE%20SHOW%20GO%20ON%26quot%3B%20but%2C%20will%20entirely%20be%20guided%20by%20Law%20Enforcement.%20They%20will%20make%20a%20decision%20shortly.%20Regardless%20of%20that%20decision%2C%20the%20evening%20will%20be%20much%20different%20than%20planned%2C%20and%20we'll%20just%2C%20plain%2C%20have%20to%20do%20it%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECBS%20senior%20White%20House%20correspondent%20Weijia%20Jiang%20took%20the%20stage%20shortly%20after%20the%20incident%20to%20say%20the%20night's%20programming%20would%20continue.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EUntil%20the%20start%20of%20the%20event%2C%20it%20was%20unclear%20when%20Trump%20would%20appear%20and%20how%20long%20he%20would%20stay.%20The%20WHCD%20dinner%20usually%20lasts%20about%20three%20hours%2C%20and%20it%20was%20uncertain%20whether%20Trump%20would%20spend%20more%20time%20at%20the%20Hilton%20than%20just%20for%20his%20speech.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Trump%20appeared%20as%20a%20private%20citizen%20and%20media%20personality%20in%202011%20and%202015%2C%20he%20notably%20boycotted%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%20during%20his%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story.%20Please%20check%20back%20for%20updates%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-evacuated-from-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777167342000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ed5efc367066d7c2971072%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-evacuated-from-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20evacuated%20from%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%20following%20what%20the%20Secret%20Service%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bshooting%20incident.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktl%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Ta