027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-openai-stargate-loans-jpmorgan-diminishing-interest-debt-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Stargate%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20%24500%20billion%20initiative%20led%20by%20Oracle%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20SoftBank%20to%20build%20AI%20infrastructure%20across%20the%20country%20and%20to%20secure%20US%20supremacy%20in%20the%20race%20to%20develop%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20the%20hype%2C%20nearby%20Michigan%20residents%20have%20concerns%20about%20the%20project.%20Protesters%20who%20gathered%20in%20Saline%20in%20December%20told%20Michigan%20Public%20Radio%20that%20they're%20worried%20about%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20electric%20grid%20and%20its%20potential%20to%20pollute%20the%20surrounding%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20protesting%20data%20centers%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ed28b3a98bc8fdc096ecbe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProtesters%20gather%20in%20downtown%20Saline%20to%20protest%20Oracle's%20new%20data%20center%20powered%20by%20DTE%2C%20Michigan's%20largest%20electric%20utility.%3Cp%3EJim%20West%2FUCG%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20magically%20went%20away%2C%20I%20would%20be%20very%20happy%20because%20I%20could%20go%20back%20to%20my%20quiet%20life%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20stand%20out%20here%20on%20the%20corner%20and%20yell%20that%20I%20don't%20want%20it%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Michigan%20resident%20Tammie%20Bruneau%20told%20Michigan%20Public%20Radio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-data-center-expansion-is-hungry-for-workers-and-electricity-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecompanies%20like%20OpenAI%3C%2