ervice%20Commission%20exam%20on%20her%20very%20first%20attempt%20without%20any%20formal%20coaching%20support.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496969%2Frupam-sonali-jpsc-jharkhand-public-service-commission-success-story%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Inspired%20by%20Avatar%E2%80%99s%20Pandora%E2%80%99%3A%20Meet%20the%20Naturalist%20Duo%20Behind%20India%E2%80%99s%201st%20Private%20Biosphere%20in%20Uttarakhand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20August%2020234.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20usually%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%3F%20Is%20it%20the%20doorbell%2C%20an%20alarm%2C%20or%20perhaps%20a%20family%20member%3F%20Now%2C%20imagine%20waking%20up%20to%20the%20calls%20of%20a%20leopard%20or%20a%20sambar%20deer%20instead!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%20Dhar%20Gupta%20experiences%20this%20every%20day%20at%20his%20biosphere%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20nestled%20in%20the%20Shivalik%20foothills%2C%20overlooking%20the%20stunning%20Raghati%20river.%20At%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337165%2Fstartup-leopard-tech-lab-helps-kerala-forest-department-combat-wildlife-crime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajaji%20Raghati%20biosphere%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20sit%20on%20a%20rock%20and%20watch%20as%20leopards%2C%20elephants%2C%20and%20leopards%20pass%20by%2C%20while%20the%20air%20is%20filled%20with%20the%20sounds%20of%20chirping%20birds%20and%20buzzing%20insects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A498044%7D%5C%