%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecolourful%20yarn%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stitched%20lovingly%20by%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20turning%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20wedding%20rituals%20into%20something%20playful%2C%20sustainable%2C%20and%20ever%20so%20slightly%20Pinterest-worthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20you%20read%20that%20right.%20The%20sacred%20garland%20exchange%2C%20long%20dominated%20by%20fresh%20roses%2C%20marigolds%20and%20orchids%2C%20is%20now%20being%20reimagined%20in%20cotton%20yarns%2C%20pearl%20beads%2C%20and%20pastel%20threads.%20Crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20the%20new%20stars%20of%20sustainable%20weddings%2C%20and%20they%20are%20fast%20gaining%20ground%20with%20couples%20who%20want%20a%20keepsake%20that%20lasts%20far%20beyond%20the%20%3Cem%3Epheras%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Instagram%20feeds%20to%20destination%20weddings%2C%20this%20handcrafted%20alternative%20is%20being%20embraced%20by%20brides%20and%20grooms%2C%20who%20are%20looking%20for%20something%20personal%2C%20unique%2C%20and%20environmentally%20conscious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20did%20this%20trend%2C%20equal%20parts%20quirky%20and%20sentimental%2C%20take%20root%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20stunning%20creation%20by%20Enchanted%20Threads%2C%20founded%20by%20Ananya%20Malhotra.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen