rl%20began%20crying%20as%20she%2C%20along%20with%20her%20family%2C%20was%20taken%20away%20to%20the%20relief%20camp%20in%20the%20rescue%20boat.%20She%20watched%20her%20house%2C%20the%20one%20that%20her%20father%20had%20taken%20a%20loan%20for%20and%20put%20his%20life%20savings%20into%20building%2C%20crumble%20to%20pieces%2C%20washed%20away%20brick%20by%20brick.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20her%20father%20consoled%20her%2C%20%E2%80%98Houses%20can%20be%20rebuilt.%20At%20least%20we%20are%20alive.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348884%2Fsenior-citizens-healthcare-boat-clinic-in-sundarbans-shis-foundation-abdul-wohab-sabitri-pal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThese%20stories%20reveal%20the%20unbreakable%20spirit%20of%20the%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Harmeet%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20take%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20time%20for%20the%20farmers%20to%20tide%20through%20the%20losses.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20animals%20are%20drowning%20and%20dying%3B%20this%20is%20leading%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20infections.%20We%20have%20our%20doctors%20across%20medical%20centres%20and%20relief%20camps%2C%20but%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20of%20waterborne%20diseases%2C%20skin%20infections%2C%20and%20diseases%20caused%20by%20mosquito%20bites%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20losses%2C%20he%20says%20they%20will%20only%20be%20able%20to%20assess%20this%20once%20the%20flood%20waters%20ebb.%20However%2C%20the%20distress%20will%20continue%20for%20farmers%20like%20Mohan%20who%20do%20not%20have%20a%20home%20to%20go%20back%20to.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20present%20that%20keeps%20him%20up%20at%20night%2C%20but%20the%20uncertain%20future.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20your%20donation%20can%20help%20bring%20comfort%20today%20and%20strength%20tomorrow%20%E2%80%94%20for%20Mohan%2C%20and%20for%20countless%20others%20like%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonate%20here.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20Donatekart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolicy%2Fpunjab-deploys-818-medical-teams-to-combat-flood-crisis-health-minister-balbir-singh%2F123675844%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E818%20medical%20teams%20deployed%20in%20flood-hit%20areas%20of%20Punjab%3A%20Health%20Minister%20Balbir%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3A%20by%20Economic%20Times%2C%20Published%20on%203%20September%202025.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757075857000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Punjab%E2%80%99s%20worst%20floods%20in%20decades%20have%20left%20lakhs%20in%20crisis.%20Your%20donation%20will%20directly%20fund%20rescue%20boats%2C%20groceries%2C%20hygiene%20kits%2C%20and%20shelter%2C%20bringing%20hope%20to%20families%20who%20have%20lost%20almost%20everything.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496899%2Fhelp-punjab-floods-relief-and-rescue-operations-donatekart-the-better-india-campaign%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2230%20Years%2C%20101%20Elephant%20Corridors%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20Blueprint%20for%20Elephant%20Protection%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeatured%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepatriot.in%2Freports%2Fwhat-our-giant-nomads-need-16992%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Patriot%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20August%202024.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20decades%20ago%2C%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%2C%20a%20youth%20could%20be%20seen%20hiding%20high%20up%20in%20one%20of%20the%20watch%20towers.%20Anyone%20passing%20by%20would%20wonder%20about%20the%20unusual%20spot%20he%20had%20picked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496783%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20answer%20lay%20in%20an%20amusing%20scene%3B%20every%20time%20the%20young%20boy%20attempted%20to%20make%20his%20way%20out%20of%20the%20tower%2C%20an%20elephant%20(camouflaged%20by%20the%20thicket%20of%20bushes)%20would%20appear%20and%20charge%20at%20him.%20And%20once%20again%2C%20the%20boy%20would%20ascend%20the%20watch%20tower%20and%20wait.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20all%20of%20four%20hours%20before%20the%20elephant%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20move%2C%20and%20the%20youth%20finally%20descended%20the%20watch%20tower%2C%20relief%20colouring%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20in%20this%20story%20was%20a%20young%20Vivek%20Menon%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20dedicated%20to%20the%20preservation%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F236243%2Fganesh-chaturthi-wild-elephant-protection-love-heroes-conservation-protection-mahout-assam-tamil-nadu-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotection%20of%20wild%20habitats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20tryst%20with%20the%20elephant%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20made%20me%20understand%20the%20animal%E2%80%99s%20strength%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles%2C%20quick%20to%20add%2C%20however%2C%20that%20his%20love%20for%20the%20wild%20and%20nature%20predates%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20singular%20story%20that%20served%20as%20inspiration%20to%20become%20a%20conservationist%2C%20Menon%20insists.%20But%20coax%20him%20a%20little%2C%20and%20he%20says%20genetics%20did%20play%20its%20role%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20from%20Kerala%2C%20the%20land%20of%20elephants%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20as%20did%20childhood%20treks.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20were%20treks%20to%20the%20Himalayas%20during%20my%20school%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Menon%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20right%20to%20say%20that%20I%20took%20to%20animals%20and%20birds%20the%20moment%20I%20was%20exposed%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20room%20resembled%20an%20animal%20shelter.%20Birds%20and%20small%20animals%20rescued%20from%20the%20wild%20and%20predatory%20hands%20found%20a%20safe%20space.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20I%20was%20doing%20them%20%5Bthe%20animals%5D%20good%20by%20bringing%20them%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20justifies.%20Today%2C%20at%2056%2C%20the%20conservationist%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20that%20same%20goodwill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHow%20many%20hours%20I%20have%20spent%20watching%20young%20bulls%20playfully%20test%20their%20strength%2C%20their%20nascent%20ivories%20never%20inflicting%20harm%2C%20their%20trunks%20loosely%20entwined%20%26amp%3B%20ears%20aflap%20while%20muscle%20and%20sinew%20grind%20against%20the%20other.%20These%20young%20mock-battles%20train%20them%20for%20later%20adult%20life!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEm9soIlOnY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FEm9soIlOnY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Vivek%20Menon%20(%40vivek4wild)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvivek4wild%2Fstatus%2F1802908763894186253%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F171244%2Fkarnataka-farmer-forest-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20for%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20when%20he%20digressed%20from%20the%20career%20plans%20his%20father%20had%20for%20him%20%E2%80%94%20a%20career%20in%20automobile%20engineering%20%E2%80%94%20and%20followed%20his%20heart%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20zoology%20laboratory%2C%20no%20one%20was%20shocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20concerning%20animals%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestion%3A%20Is%20there%20a%20better%20way%20to%20interview%20a%20conservationist%20than%20reaching%20him%20through%20a%20Zoom%20call%20while%20he%20is%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20South%20African%20jungle%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbsolutely%20not%3B%20just%20what%20is%20needed%20to%20add%20essence%20to%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMenon%E2%80%99s%20excitement%20was%20palpable.%20As%20senior%20advisor%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98International%20Fund%20for%20Animal%20Welfare%E2%80%99%20for%20years%20now%2C%20he%20was%20in%20the%20Southern%20African%20country%20assisting%20in%20an%20operation%20that%20involved%20radio%20collaring%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F260553%2Fwildlife-conservation-elephants-save-school-teacher-hero-west-bengal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelephants%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20process%20in%20which%20a%20collar%20with%20an%20attached%20radio%20transmitter%20is%20put%20on%20an%20animal%20so%20that%20its%20movements%20in%20its%20natural%20habitat%20can%20be%20remotely%20monitored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20he%20jokingly%20adds%2C%20my%20interview%20call%20is%20interrupting%20something%20very%20important%20that%20he%E2%80%99d%20otherwise%20be%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20watching%20150%20elephants%20against%20the%20setting%20sun%20in%20Zimbabwe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%20has%20watched%20Menon%20around%20elephants%20would%20testify%20that%20the%20two%20share%20a%20bond.%20He%20understands%20them.%20And%20the%20relationship%20is%20reciprocal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubstantial%20proof%20of%20his%20love%20for%20the%20wild%20lies%20in%20the%20five%20organisations%20that%20he%20has%20created%20%E2%80%94%20TRAFFIC%20India%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wildlife%20trade%20monitoring%20network%3B%20NGO%20Srishti%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20founded%20to%20protect%20the%20environment%20in%20Delhi%3B%20Delhi%20Bird%20Club%3B%20Venu%20Menon%20Animal%20Allies%20Foundation%3B%20and%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20(WTI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wild%20elephant%20herd%20in%20Keonjhar%2C%20Odisha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360931%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20wild%20elephant%20herd%20in%20Keonjhar%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPicture%20a%20world%20where%20trade%20in%20wild%20plants%20and%20animals%20is%20managed%20at%20sustainable%20levels%20without%20damaging%20the%20integrity%20of%20ecological%20systems.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20TRAFFIC%20India%20has%20attempted%20to%20do%20since%20the%20outset.%20Menon%20who%20co-founded%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F48373%2Fwildlife-trade-trafficking-india-humane-society%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20trade%20monitoring%20%3C%2Fa%3Enetwork%20with%20his%20colleague%20and%20legendary%20conservationist%20Ashok%20Kumar%2C%20emphasises%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20resolve%20to%20bust%20poaching%20amid%20other%20illegal%20activities.%20The%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20work%20also%20extends%20to%20the%20fight%20against%20illegal%20international%20ivory%20trade.%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20work%20earned%20him%20the%20RG%20Samsara%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20activism%20is%20important%2C%20this%20biologist%20believes%20in%20shedding%20an%20equal%20spotlight%20on%20creating%20impact%20through%20policy%20frameworks.%20As%20Chair%20of%20the%20Asian%20Elephant%20Specialist%20Group%20for%20the%20IUCN%20(International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature)%20for%20the%20past%2012%20years%2C%20Menon%20elaborates%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20work%20in%20advising%20various%20governments%20on%20%E2%80%9Cdoing%20things%20right%20for%20elephants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20includes%20bringing%20out%20scientific%20work%2C%20guidelines%2C%20and%20manuals.%20It%20also%20includes%20planning%20linear%20infrastructure%3B%20highways%2C%20railways%2C%20road%20passes%2C%20and%20power%20lines%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20the%20elephants%20are%20allowed%20to%20pass%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20segues%20into%20the%20topic%20of%20identifying%20and%20protecting%20elephant%20corridors%2C%20a%20brainchild%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20overarching%20goal%20being%20to%20secure%20a%20%E2%80%98rite%20of%20passage%E2%80%99%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F188598%2Felephant-doctor-assam-treats-hundreds-wildlife-hero-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig%20mammals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20WTI%20along%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20top%20scientists%20have%20identified%20and%20surveyed%20101%20such%20functional%20corridors%20across%2011%20states%20for%20the%2029%2C000%20odd%20Asian%20Elephants%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20a%20spare%20bedroom%20project%20to%20a%20phenomenal%20trust%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202023%20study%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20Wildlife%20and%20Biodiversity%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20corridors%20are%20short%20strips%20of%20forests%20that%20link%20two%20larger%20parts%20of%20the%20forest%3B%20like%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccontinuous%20two-dimensional%20landscape%20structure%20that%20interconnects%20two%20or%20more%20previously%20linked%20areas%20of%20animal%20habitats%E2%80%9D.%20These%20enable%20the%20animals%20to%20disperse%2C%20reduce%20their%20risk%20of%20separation%20and%20make%20habitat%20rehabilitation%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20explored%20how%20anthropogenic%20stress%2C%20the%20development%20of%20roads%20and%20railways%2C%20and%20hydroelectric%20projects%20are%20hampering%20these%20corridors.%20The%20problem%20is%20compounded%20by%20multiple%20forests%20being%20turned%20into%20croplands%20by%20the%20farming%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-500x417.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20walking%20bear%20cubs%20to%20reintroducing%20orphaned%20elephant%20calves%20back%20into%20the%20wild%2C%20Vivek%20Menon%20is%20championing%20wildlife%20conservation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-500x417.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-300x250.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-768x641.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-1536x1281.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-1200x1001.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-150x125.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275.jpeg%201822w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360936%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22417%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFrom%20walking%20bear%20cubs%20to%20reintroducing%20orphaned%20elephant%20calves%20back%20into%20the%20wild%2C%20Vivek%20Menon%20is%20championing%20wildlife%20conservation%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2025%20years%2C%20WTI%20has%20attempted%20to%20better%20the%20narrative%20for%20wildlife%20across%20species.%20Their%20impact%20is%20resounding%20%E2%80%94%20campaigning%20for%20the%20whale%20shark%20to%20be%20made%20the%20first%20fish%20to%20be%20protected%20under%20the%20Wildlife%20(Protection)%20Act%2C%201972%2C%20in%20India%2C%20exposing%20the%20illegal%20mongoose%20hairbrush%20trade%2C%20assisting%20in%20the%20seizure%20of%20over%20275%20wildlife%20articles%20including%20tiger%20bones%20and%20bear%20bile%2C%20and%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F65156%2Fpangolin-conservation-wildlife-sos%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epangolin%20trafficking%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20attempts%20to%20curb%20illegal%20trade%20of%20the%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20organisation%20masks%20its%20humble%20beginnings.%20But%20Vivek%20Menon%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20forgotten%20these.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20as%20a%20team%20of%20three%20people%20in%20a%20spare%20room%20of%20my%20house.%20Each%20of%20us%20invested%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20The%20investment%20was%20secondary.%20Passion%20was%20what%20drove%20WTI%20to%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMenon%20has%20a%20piece%20of%20advice%20that%20he%20believes%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20ensuring%20a%20better%20place%20for%20wildlife%2C%20including%20elephants%2C%20on%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFirm%20anti-poaching%20policies%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20spent%20the%20better%20part%20of%20his%20life%20as%20a%20conservationist%20training%20Indian%20forest%20guards%2C%20rangers%2C%20and%20paramilitary%20forces%20on%20anti-poaching%20activities%20and%20smuggling%20techniques%2C%20Menon%20has%20witnessed%20the%20network%20close%20up.%20But%20he%20insists%20that%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20any%20illegal%20activity%2C%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20way%20of%20curbing%20it%20completely.%20%E2%80%9COne%20can%20only%20lessen%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20end%2C%20Menon%20says%20the%20forest%20guards%20are%20often%20the%20first%20line%20of%20defence%20to%20stop%20illegal%20trade.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20should%20be%20trained%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F233468%2Findia-tigers-save-vultures-how-to-wildlife-conservation-environment-rajasthan-ranthambhore-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanti-poaching%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20in%20cases%20of%20the%20animal%20being%20poached%20despite%20precautionary%20measures%2C%20the%20border%20staff%20should%20be%20trained%20to%20ensure%20that%20smuggling%20of%20ivory%20is%20not%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReducing%20man-animal%20conflict%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrop%20raiding%20and%20property%20destruction%20are%20the%20prime%20factors%20that%20cause%20elephant-human%20conflict%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EInternational%20Fund%20for%20Animal%20Welfare%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20study%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20in%20India%2C%20100%20elephants%20die%20annually%20from%20conflict%20with%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20creating%20elephant%20corridors%20across%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360941%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20creating%20elephant%20corridors%20across%20India%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%2C%20says%20Menon%2C%20is%20exacerbated%20by%20lack%20of%20space.%20%E2%80%9CAn%20elephant%20is%20a%20big%2C%20intelligent%20social%20nomad.%20It%20has%20to%20move%3B%20it%20has%20to%20do%20so%20in%20groups%3B%20and%20it%20is%20intelligent.%20Whatever%20stands%20in%20its%20way%20it%20will%20destroy%20to%20move.%20One%20has%20to%20respect%20it%20and%20give%20it%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreate%20elephant%20corridors%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20perfect%20world%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F141120%2Fwildlife-sos-bears-elephants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehabitats%20of%20elephants%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20contiguous%2C%20Menon%20points%20out.%20%E2%80%9CElephants%20would%20be%20able%20to%20move%20from%20the%20Himalayas%20to%20the%20South%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%20But%20he%20adds%20that%20the%20reason%20this%20is%20no%20longer%20possible%20is%20because%20the%20mammals%20now%20share%20the%20ground%20with%20people%20and%20their%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20WTI%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20demarcate%20the%20elephant%20corridors%20and%20push%20for%20them%20to%20be%20declared%20as%20protected%20zones%2C%20Menon%20says%2C%20they%20relied%20on%20elephant%20footpaths.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20mapped%20these%20and%20showed%20it%20in%20a%20publication%2C%20explaining%20why%20they%20were%20integral%20pieces%20of%20land%20that%20connected%20with%20the%20different%20habitats.%20We%20delineated%20these%20on%20paper%2C%20asking%20the%20Government%20to%20protect%20these%20elephant%20corridors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20learnings%20they%20had%20during%20the%20project%2C%20Menon%20says%20the%20protection%20of%20elephant%20corridors%20can%20be%20done%20in%20four%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20model%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20the%20community%20model%20in%20the%20Northeast%2C%20which%20has%20been%20on%20for%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20model%20focuses%20on%20land%20being%20kept%20aside%20by%20the%20community%20for%20elephants%20to%20move.%20It%20also%20involves%20rewarding%20the%20community%20with%20some%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20Menon%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20model%20is%20pushing%20the%20Government%20to%20acquire%20land%20and%20conduct%20linear%20infrastructure%20mitigations.%20The%20third%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20to%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F180063%2Fkerala-woman-animal-rights-elephants-inspirational%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20community%20of%20people%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20are%20trained%20in%20keeping%20an%20eye%20out%20for%20elephant%20movements.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20in%20Kaziranga%2C%20there%20are%20groups%20of%20young%20boys%20who%20are%20on%20alert.%20They%20stop%20cars%20to%20allow%20the%20elephants%20to%20cross.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20is%20to%20relocate%20villages.%20This%20%E2%80%9Clast-ditch%20effort%E2%80%9D%20is%20only%20resorted%20to%20in%20areas%20where%20people%20have%20settled%20right%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20elephant%20corridors%20and%20elephants%20are%20killing%20them%20and%20not%20letting%20crops%20grow%2C%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-500x672.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vivek%20Menon%20and%20elephants%20share%20a%20bond%20of%20love%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-500x672.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-223x300.jpg%20223w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-768x1033.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-1142x1536.jpg%201142w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-1523x2048.jpg%201523w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-1200x1614.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-150x202.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360946%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVivek%20Menon%20and%20elephants%20share%20a%20bond%20of%20love%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERescue%20and%20rehabilitation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty%20years%20ago%20when%20Menon%20and%20his%20team%20started%20the%20rescue%20and%20rehabilitation%20of%20orphan%20elephant%20calves%20to%20reintroduce%20them%20into%20the%20wild%2C%20people%20discouraged%20the%20idea.%20But%20the%20conservationist%20points%20to%20the%2050%20percent%20success%20rate%20they%20have%20achieved%20as%20a%20nod%20to%20their%20persistence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPutting%20policies%20in%20place%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20Menon%20received%20the%20Whitley%20Award%20for%20a%20project%20focusing%20on%20%E2%80%98Monitoring%20of%20Elephant%20Poaching%20and%20Ivory%20Trade%20in%20India%20and%20Asia%E2%80%99.%20Reaching%20this%20zenith%20of%20excellence%20gave%20tremendous%20backing%20to%20his%20work%20in%20putting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F190973%2Findia-first-wildlife-underpass-kanha-pench-corridor-tigers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20corridors%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20when%20India%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Court%20earmarked%20the%20Sigur%20Plateau%20%E2%80%94%20which%20sees%20the%20movement%20of%20around%206%2C300%20Asiatic%20Elephants%20%E2%80%94%20as%20an%20elephant%20corridor%2C%20%3Cem%3EWhitley%20Fund%20for%20Nature%3C%2Fem%3E%20notes%20how%20the%20apex%20court%20used%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20evidence%20of%20the%20benefits%20to%20both%20wildlife%20and%20people.%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20created%20ripples%3B%20shaping%20the%20crux%20of%20wildlife%20policies%20as%20we%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20can%20sit%20and%20listen%20to%20him%20for%20hours.%20But%20I%20know%20he%20has%20somewhere%20to%20be%3B%20I%E2%80%99m%20keeping%20a%20hundred%20and%20fifty%20of%20his%20jungle%20friends%20waiting%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20one%20last%20question%20before%20you%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20say%2C%20unable%20to%20stop%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20you%20see%20in%20them%20that%20connects%20you%20to%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20near%20persons%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20them%20in%20terms%20of%20conscience%2C%20memory%2C%20and%20intellect.%20They%20are%20very%20similar%20to%20us.%20They%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20understand%20my%20words%20or%20my%20language.%20But%20they%20understand%20me%20in%20other%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20before%20he%20concludes%20our%20conversation%20to%20head%20to%20the%20place%20where%20he%20feels%20most%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20amid%20the%20elephants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wildlife-biodiversity.com%2Findex.php%2Fjwb%2Farticle%2Fdownload%2F223%2F310%2F1074%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElephant%20Corridor%20loss%20due%20to%20anthropogenic%20stress%20%E2%80%93%20a%20study%20of%20change%20in%20forest%20cover%20using%20satellite%20data%20in%20the%20Sonitpur%20District%2C%20Assam%2C%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3A%20by%20Journal%20of%20Wildlife%20and%20Biodiversity%2C%20Published%20on%207%20June%202022.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifaw.org%2Finternational%2Fjournal%2Fhuman-elephant-conflict-major-threat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuman-elephant%20conflict%3A%20What%20it%20is%20and%20why%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20major%20threat%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3A%20by%20IFAW%2C%20Published%20on%2020%20July%202023.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhitleyaward.org%2Fwinners%2Felephant-poaching-ivory-trade-india-asia%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%25202020%252C%2520India%2527s%2520Supreme%2520Court%2Cto%2520both%2520wildlife%2520and%2520people.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Monitoring%20of%20elephant%20poaching%20and%20ivory%20trade%2C%20India%20and%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3A%20by%20Whitley%20Fund%20for%20Nature.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757071800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http